\c 8
\s Temberi inotsaurirwa Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Panguva iyoyo Soromoni wakaunganidza vakuru vaIsraeri, misoro yese yemarudzi, machinda emadzibaba evana vaIsraeri, kuenda kuna mambo Soromoni paJerusarema, kuti vakwidze areka yesungano yaJehovha kubva muguta raDhavhidhi, iro Ziyoni.
\v 2 Varume vese vaIsraeri ndokuungana kuna mambo Soromoni pamutambo pamwedzi weEtanimi, unova mwedzi wechinomwe.
\v 3 Vakuru vese vaIsraeri ndokuuya; vapristi vakasimudza areka.
\v 4 Zvino vakakwidza areka yaJehovha, netende rekusangana, nemidziyo yese mitsvene yaiva mutende; vapristi neVaRevhi vakakwidzawo izvozvo.
\v 5 Zvino mambo Soromoni neungano yese yaIsraeri yakaunganira kwaari, vaiva naye pamberi peareka, vachibaira makwai nenzombe, zvisingagoni kuraviwa kana kuverengwa neuwandu.
\v 6 Zvino vapristi vakapinza areka yesungano yaJehovha panzvimbo yayo, panzvimbo yeshoko yeimba, panzvimbo tsvene-tsvene, pazasi pemapapiro emakerubhi.
\v 7 Nokuti makerubhi akatandavadza mapapiro maviri pamusoro penzvimbo yeareka; makerubhi ndokufukidza areka nezvibatiso zvayo kubva kumusoro.
\v 8 Zvino vakarebesa zvibatiso kuti misoro yezvibatiso ionekere panzvimbo tsvene pamberi penzvimbo yeshoko; asi yaiva isingaonekeri nechekunze; uye aripo kusvika nhasi.
\v 9 Muareka maiva musina chinhu kunze kwemahwendefa maviri emabwe, Mozisi aaiva aisamo paHorebhu, Jehovha paakaitapo \add sungano\add* nevana vaIsraeri pakubuda kwavo panyika yeEgipita.
\v 10 Zvino zvakaitika pakubuda kwevapristi kubva panzvimbo tsvene, kuti gore rakazadza imba yaJehovha.
\v 11 Naizvozvo vapristi vaiva vasingagoni kumira kuti vashumire nekuda kwegore; nokuti kubwinya kwaJehovha kwakazadza imba yaJehovha.
\s Mashoko aSoromoni nekunyengetera kwake
\p
\v 12 Panguva iyoyo Soromoni akati: Jehovha wakati achagara murima gobvu.
\v 13 Ndakuvakirai zvekukuvakirai imba, nzvimbo yekugara, nzvimbo yakamiswa yekugara kwenyu rinhi narinhi.
\v 14 Zvino mambo akatendeudza chiso chake, ndokuropafadza ungano yese yaIsraeri; uye ungano yese yaIsraeri yaiva yakasimuka.
\v 15 Zvino wakati: Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri ngaakudzwe, iye wakataura nemuromo wake kuna Dhavhidhi baba vangu, uye akazadzisa neruoko rwake, achiti:
\v 16 Kubva pazuva randakabudisa vanhu vangu Israeri kubva muEgipita, handina kusarudza guta kubva pamarudzi ese aIsraeri kuvaka imba, kuti zita rangu rigarepo; asi ndakasarudza Dhavhidhi ave pamusoro pevanhu vangu Israeri.
\v 17 Zvino zvaiva mumoyo maDhavhidhi baba vangu kuvakira zita raJehovha Mwari waIsraeri imba.
\v 18 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Dhavhidhi baba vangu: Sezvo zvanga zviri mumoyo mako kuvakira zita rangu imba, waita zvakanaka kuti zvanga zviri mumoyo mako.
\v 19 Zvakadaro iwe haungavaki imba iyo, asi mwanakomana wako achabuda muchiuno chako, iye achavakira zita rangu imba.
\v 20 Zvino Jehovha wasimbisa shoko rake raakataura, nokuti ndamuka pachinzvimbo chaDhavhidhi baba vangu, ndokugara pachigaro cheushe chaIsraeri, Jehovha sezvaakataura, uye ndavakira zita raJehovha Mwari waIsraeri imba.
\v 21 Zvino ndaisamo nzvimbo yeareka mune sungano yaJehovha yaakaita nemadzibaba edu paakavabudisa panyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Soromoni wakamira pamberi pearitari yaJehovha pakatarisana neungano yese yaIsraeri, ndokutandavadzira maoko ake kumatenga,
\v 23 ndokuti: Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri, hakuna Mwari wakaita semwi kumatenga kumusoro kana panyika pasi, anochengeta sungano netsitsi nevaranda venyu vanofamba pamberi penyu nemoyo yavo yese.
\v 24 Makachengetera muranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu zvamakataura kwaari; uye makataura nemuromo wenyu, ndokuzvizadzisa neruoko rwenyu, sanhasi.
\v 25 Naizvozvo ikozvino, Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, chengetedzerai muranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu zvamakamutaurira muchiti: Hakungashaikwi munhu kwauri pamberi pangu achagara pachigaro cheushe chaIsraeri, koga kana vana vako vakachengeta nzira yavo kufamba pamberi pangu sezvawakafamba pamberi pangu.
\v 26 Zvino ikozvino, Mwari waIsraeri, dai shoko renyu rasimbiswa ramakataura kumuranda wenyu Dhavhidhi baba vangu.
\v 27 Asi zvirokwazvo Mwari achagara panyika here? Tarira, matenga, nematenga ematenga haangakuringanii; kuzoti idiki sei imba ino yandakavaka!
\v 28 Zvakadaro tendeukirai kumunyengetero wemuranda wenyu, nekukumbira kwake, Jehovha Mwari wangu, kuti munzwe kuchema nekumunyengetero wemuranda wenyu waanonyengetera pamberi penyu nhasi.
\v 29 Kuti meso enyu azarurikire imba iyi siku nesikati nzvimbo yamakati nezvayo: Zita rangu richavapo kuteerera kumunyengetero wemuranda wenyu waanonyengetera akatarisa kunzvimbo ino.
\v 30 Zvino inzwai kukumbira kwemuranda wenyu, nekwevanhu venyu Israeri pavanonyengetera vakatarisa kunzvimbo ino. Hongu inzwai imwi, muri panzvimbo yenyu yekugara kumatenga, uye pamunonzwa muregerere.
\p
\v 31 Kana munhu upi neupi atadzira umwe wake, mhiko ikaiswa pamusoro pake kuti amupikise, uye mhiko iuye pamberi pearitari yenyu muimba ino,
\v 32 zvino inzwai imwi muri kumatenga, mugoita uye mugotonga varanda venyu, muti wakaipa wakaipa, kupa nzira yake kumusoro wake, kururamisira wakarurama, kumupa zvinoenderana nekururama kwake.
\p
\v 33 Kana vanhu venyu Israeri vakarohwa pamberi pevavengi nokuti vakutadzirai, uye vakadzokerazve kwamuri ndokutenda zita renyu ndokunyengetera, uye vakaita chikumbiro kwamuri muimba ino;
\v 34 zvino inzwai imwi muri kumatenga, mugoregerera chivi chevanhu venyu Israeri, mugovadzoserazve kunyika yamakapa madzibaba avo.
\p
\v 35 Kana matenga akavharwa, zvino kukasava nemvura nokuti vakakutadzirai; kana vakanyengetera vakatarisa kunzvimbo ino, vakatenda zita renyu, vakatendeuka pazvivi zvavo, pamunovatambudza;
\v 36 zvino inzwai imwi muri kumatenga, mugoregerera chivi chevaranda venyu, nechevanhu venyu Israeri, nokuti munovadzidzisa nzira yakanaka yavangafamba nayo; mupe mvura panyika yenyu yamakapa vanhu venyu kuti ive nhaka.
\p
\v 37 Kana pakava nenzara panyika, kana pane denda, kupisa, nyunje mhashu, kana kune mhondoro, kana muvengi wavo akavakomba panyika ine maguta avo; kana dambudziko ripi kana hosha ipi;
\v 38 munyengetero upi neupi nekukumbira kupi nekupi zvinoitwa chero nani, nevanhu venyu vese Israeri, vachaziva uyo neuyo dambudziko remoyo wake, akatandavadzira maoko ake kuimba iyi;
\v 39 zvino inzwai imwi muri kumatenga, nzvimbo yenyu yekugara yakamiswa, mugoregerera, uye muite, mugopa umwe neumwe zvichienderana nenzira dzake dzese, moyo wake wamunoziva, nokuti ndimwi mega munoziva moyo wevese vana vevanhu;
\v 40 kuti vakutyei mazuva ese avachararama pachiso chenyika yamakapa madzibaba edu.
\p
\v 41 Zvinowo mutorwa, asiri wevanhu venyu Israeri, asi anobva kunyika iri kure nekuda kwezita renyu.
\v 42 Nokuti vachanzwa zvezita renyu guru uye zveruoko rwenyu rwakasimba uye zvechanza chenyu cha katandavadzwa kana akauya ndokunyengetera akatarira kuimba ino;
\v 43 inzwai imwi muri kumatenga, nzvimbo yenyu yekugara yakamiswa, mugoita zvinoenderana nezvese mutorwa zvaanokudanirai, kuti marudzi ese epanyika azive zita renyu, akutyei, sevanhu vako Israeri, uye kuti vazive kuti zita renyu rinodanwa pamusoro peimba ino yandakavaka.
\p
\v 44 Kana vanhu venyu vakabuda kuhondo kurwisa muvengi wavo, nenzira yamunovatuma nayo, ndokunyengetera kuna Jehovha vakatarisa kuguta ramakasarudza, nekuimba yandakavakira zita renyu,
\v 45 ipapo inzwai imwi muri kumatenga munyengetero wavo nemukumbiro wavo, uye muvaruramisire.
\v 46 Kana vakakutadzirai, nokuti hakuna munhu asingatadzi, uye mukavatsamwira, ndokuvapa kuvavengi vavo kuti vatapi vavo vavatapire kunyika yemuvengi, kure kana pedo;
\v 47 kana vakazozvifunga kunyika kwavakatapirwa, vakadzokazve, vakakumbira kwamuri munyika yevatapi vavo, vachiti: Tatadza, uye tatsauka, taita zvakaipa;
\v 48 zvino vakadzokera kwamuri nemoyo wavo wese, uye nemweya wavo wese munyika yevavengi vavo vakavatapa, ndokunyengetera kwamuri vakatarisa kunyika yavo yamakapa kumadzibaba avo, guta ramakasarudza neimba yandakavakira zita renyu.
\v 49 Ipapo Inzwai imwi muri kumatenga nzvimbo yenyu yekugara, munyengetero wavo nemukumbiro wavo, uye muvaruramisire;
\v 50 uye muregerere vanhu venyu vakakutadzirai, nekudarika kwavo kwese, kwavakadarika nako kwamuri; muvape tsitsi pamberi pevakavatapa, kuti vave netsitsi kwavari.
\v 51 Nokuti ivo vanhu venyu nenhaka yenyu yamakabudisa kubva muEgipita pakati pevira rematare;
\v 52 kuti meso enyu azarukire kumukumbiro wemuranda wenyu, uye kumukumbiro wevanhu venyu Israeri, kuvateerera pakuchema kwavo kwese kwamuri.
\v 53 Nokuti imwi makavaparadzanise kuva nhaka yenyu kubva pamarudzi ese enyika, sezvamakataura neruoko rwaMozisi muranda wenyu, pamakabudisa madzibaba edu kubva muEgipita, Ishe Jehovha.
\p
\v 54 Zvino kwakati Soromoni apedza kunyengetera munyengetero uyu wese nemukumbiro kuna Jehovha, wakasimuka kubva pamberi pearitari yaJehovha pakupfugama nemabvi ake nemaoko ake akatandavadzirwa kumatenga.
\v 55 Zvino wakamira ndokuropafadza ungano yese yaIsraeri nenzwi guru, achiti,
\v 56 Jehovha ngaakudzwe wakapa vanhu vake Israeri zororo zvichienderana nezvese zvaakavimbisa, hakuna kuwa shoko rimwe pachivimbiso chake chese chakanaka chaakavimbisa neruoko rwaMozisi muranda wake.
\v 57 Jehovha Mwari wedu ngaave nesu, sezvaaiva nemadzibaba edu; ngaarege kutisiya, kana kutirega;
\v 58 kuti arerekesere moyo yedu kwaari, kufamba munzira dzake dzese, uye kuchengeta mirairo yake yese, nezvimiso zvake, nemitongo yake, zvaakaraira madzibaba edu.
\v 59 Zvino mashoko awa andakakumbira nawo pamberi paJehovha, ngaave pedo naJehovha Mwari wedu masikati neusiku, kuti aruramisire nyaya yemuranda wake, nenyaya yevanhu vake Israeri, nyaya yezuva pazuva rayo;
\v 60 kuti vanhu vese venyika vazive kuti Jehovha ndiMwari, hakuna umwe.
\v 61 Naizvozvo moyo yenyu ngaive yakaperedzerwa kuna Jehovha Mwari wedu, kufamba muzvimiso zvake, nekuchengeta mirairo yake sanhasi.
\p
\v 62 Zvino mambo naIsraeri wese anaye ndokupa zvibairo pamberi paJehovha.
\v 63 Zvino Soromoni wakapa chibairo chezvipo zvekuyananisa, zvaakapa kuna Jehovha, nzombe zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri, nemakwai zvuru zana nemakumi maviri. Mambo wevana vaIsraeri vese ndokutsaurira Jehovha imba.
\v 64 Nezuva iroro mambo wakatsvenesa pakati pechivanze chaiva pamberi peimba yaJehovha, nokuti ipapo wakapa chipo chinopiswa, nechipo chechidyiwa, nemafuta ezvipo zvekuyananisa; nokuti aritari yendarira yaiva pamberi paJehovha yakange iri diki zvikuru kuringana chipo chinopiswa, nechipo chechidyiwa, nemafuta ezvipo zvekuyananisa.
\p
\v 65 Zvino nenguva iyo Soromoni wakaita mabiko, naIsraeri wese pamwe naye, ungano huru, kubva pakupinda paHamati kusvika parukova rweEgipita, pamberi paJehovha Mwari wedu, mazuva manomwe nemazuva manomwe, mazuva gumi nemana.
\v 66 Pazuva rerusere wakaendesa vanhu, ivo ndokurumbidza mambo, ndokuenda kumatende avo nemoyo ine rufaro, ichifara nezvakanaka zvese Jehovha zvaakaitira Dhavhidhi muranda wake naIsraeri vanhu vake.